data.description: Superb ranch home in Northbrook that is placed on almost half acre land. This 6 bedroom 3.5 bathroom home features many updates since it was remodeled in 2017. Perfect for entertaining with the a massive private yard. This home features new hardwood floors throughout on the first floor. Beautiful white kitchen with granite counter tops, farm style sink, stone blacksplash, and stainless-steel appliances. This home does not only have just one fireplace but two which are located in the Family and Living room with a stunning mosaic stone wall. The fully finished basement has two bedrooms and a full bathroom perfect for guest. Some new features in the home included: Water heater, doors, windows, service well system, plumbing, 2 sump pump with back battery, siding, garage door and transmitters. No expense was spared and the craftmanship shows. Convenient location to schools, highway, malls, and stores.
